Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Little Ben
Description: A replica of Big Ben in London that was built at 1892.

Name: Odaiba Statue of Liberty
Description: A replica of Statue of Liberty in Tokyo that was built at 1998 as a tribute to the friendship between Japan and France.

Name: Leaning Tower of Niles
Description: A replica of Leaning Tower of Pisa in Illinois that was built at 1934; Niles later became a sister city with Pisa.

Name: Eiffel Tower Las Vegas
Description: A replica of Eiffel Tower in Las Vegas that was built at 1997 for a casino hotel.

Name: Foamhenge
Description: A replica of Stonehenge in Virginia that was built at 2004.
